The related publication (by Yang H. et al, 2020) reports newly discovered properties of T30695, such as the insertion of Zn<sub>2+</sub> in other porphyrins, and the utilization of Pb<sub>2+</sub> as a substrate.
buffer: 100 mM Tris-HCl pH 7.5, 200 mM NaOAc, 25 mM KOAc, 10 mM Mg(OAc)2
